        public VirtualReality(double f0,
                      double f1,
                      double f2,
                      double ql,
                      double frames)
        Constructor to initialize the three previous frame processing times, current quality level of the video, and the target frame time It also initializes all the threshold values
        Parameters:
        f0 - - processing time for frame 0 (two frames ago) in ms
        f1 - - processing time for frame 1 (frame before last) in ms
        f2 - - processing time for frame 2 (last frame) in ms
        ql - - quality level of the video (ranges from 1 to 10)
        frames - - desired frames per second pre-condition: 1 <= ql <= 10 pre-condition: f0, f1, f2 > 0
